column2: SELECT TOP #   a.OBJID AS OBJID,   a.RA AS RA,   a.DEC AS DEC,      /* Photoz */      /*   phz.objID AS sdssid,   phz.z AS zph,   phz.zErr AS e_zph,   */      /* SpecObjAll */      sp.specObjID AS specObjID_sdss,   sp.bestObjID AS bestObjID_sdss,   sp.fluxObjID AS fluxObjID_sdss,   sp.targetObjID AS targetObjID_sdss,   sp.ra AS RA_sdss,   sp.dec AS DEC_sdss,   sp.z AS zsp,   sp.zErr AS e_zsp,   sp.class AS class,   sp.subClass AS subClass,   sp.zWarning AS zWarning,            /* PhotoObjAll */      /*   ph.objID AS sdssid,   ph.ra AS RA_sdss,   ph.dec AS DEC_sdss,   ph.mode AS mode,   ph.probPSF AS probPSF,  propability that object is the star    ph.modelMag_u AS umag,   ph.modelMag_g AS gmag,   ph.modelMag_r AS rmag,   ph.modelMag_i AS imag,   ph.modelMag_z AS zmag,   ph.modelMagErr_u AS e_umag,   ph.modelMagErr_g AS e_gmag,   ph.modelMagErr_r AS e_rmag,   ph.modelMagErr_i AS e_imag,   ph.modelMagErr_z AS e_zmag,   */      n.distance AS angDist    /* into mydb.AKARIx3#SDSS1#_zsp_crac */    from   MyDB.akari AS a   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( a.RA, a.DEC, #) AS n   /* LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as ph ON n.objid = ph.objid */   LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS sp ON n.objid = sp.specObjID   /* LEFT JOIN Photoz AS phz ON n.objid = phz.objid */    where   a.OBJID < #
